label day9s3:

    #The music here should fit a melancholic tone
    scene hospitalhallway with dissolve
    play music bgmsad1intro noloop fadeout 1.0
    queue music bgmsad1loop loop
    "Once again, I find myself heading down the hospital halls."

    "However, this time I see something I didn’t expect."

    "Though in hindsight, I probably should have."

    voice "9-3-1.mp3" #potato
    pro "Mom?"

    show mom sad2

    voice "9-3-2.mp3" #kaito
    mom "...Oh. Hi, Emily. You’re here to... to see Alex, right?"

    voice "9-3-3.mp3" #potato
    pro "Yeah. You saw him, then?"

    voice "9-3-4.mp3" #kaito
    mom "Mhm. I was just heading out, so... bye."

    hide mom sad2

    voice "9-3-5.mp3" #potato
    pro "Uh... bye?"

    "There’s a lot I need to ask her about, but... now doesn’t really seem like the time."

    "Plus, if it leads to an argument, I might get kicked out."

    "I’ll just let it go and head to Alex’s room."

    #Transition
    scene hospitalroom with dissolve
    show bro sad1

    voice "9-3-6.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Hey, Emily."

    voice "9-3-7.mp3" #potato
    pro "Hey. Did Mom come through here just now?"

    voice "9-3-8.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Yeah, I guess."

    voice "9-3-9.mp3" #potato
    pro "You... guess?"

    voice "9-3-10.mp3" #kujira
    bro "I mean, physically she came in here, but... she didn’t do much, and wasn’t really herself."
    hide bro sad1
    show bro sad2
    voice "9-3-11.mp3" #kujira
    bro "I half expected her to chew me out for causing everyone trouble again, but she just... apologized a few times and left."

    voice "9-3-12.mp3" #kujira
    bro "If you hadn’t come in, I probably would have passed it off as a dream."

    voice "9-3-13.mp3" #potato
    pro "Nah. A dream mom would have come in, talked about your life, supported you, and given you a box of cookies."

    voice "9-3-14.mp3" #potato
    pro "Only a real one could act as weird as her."

    voice "9-3-15.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Heh. That’s a good point."

    "I would know, after all."

    voice "9-3-16.mp3" #kujira
    bro "But I kind of get where she’s coming from."

    voice "9-3-17.mp3" #potato
    pro "Seriously?"

    voice "9-3-18.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Mom is always talking about giving us bright futures and all that, right?"

    voice "9-3-19.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Sometimes it seems like she’s a villain from right out of a kids’ movie, but I do think she actually cares."

    voice "9-3-20.mp3" #kujira
    bro "She’s just really damn bad at it."

    voice "9-3-21.mp3" #potato
    pro "Now that you mention it, guess I haven’t really spent time thinking about her point of view."

    voice "9-3-22.mp3" #kujira
    bro "It doesn’t matter that much. If you treat people like shit, even if you think it’s for a good reason, you’re still treating people like shit, right?"

    voice "9-3-23.mp3" #kujira
    bro "But good intentions mean she might come to her senses."

    voice "9-3-24.mp3" #kujira
    bro "I think that’s what’s happening now. If she did hate us, she wouldn’t be so torn up about this."

    voice "9-3-25.mp3" #kujira
    bro "But if she really does care about our futures and all that, then... then the risk of one of us not <i>having</i> a future..."

    voice "9-3-26.mp3" #kujira
    bro "I feel like I did something horrible to her."

    voice "9-3-27.mp3" #potato
    pro "...I can’t deny that."
    hide bro sad2
    show bro sad1
    voice "9-3-28.mp3" #potato
    pro "But I think this is a good opportunity to move forward."

    voice "9-3-29.mp3" #potato
    pro "I think, for the first time, she might be able to understand where we’re coming from... and maybe we can do the same for her."
    hide bro sad1
    show bro sad2
    voice "9-3-30.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Do you seriously think that’s possible anymore?"

    voice "9-3-31.mp3" #potato
    pro "I don’t know, but I can’t let things end here."

    voice "9-3-32.mp3" #potato
    pro "You and Maria deserve better than this."

    "Alex freezes up at the mention of our sister. He looks away, his face scrunched up in guilt"

    voice "9-3-33.mp3" #potato
    pro "Alex… Maria’s been asking about you. She wants to see you. Are you sure you don’t want me to bring her here next time?"

    voice "9-3-34.mp3" #kujira
    bro "No, I’m… I’m not ready."

    voice "9-3-35.mp3" #potato
    pro "Then, do you wanna talk about what happened?"
    show bro sad2
    "He gives a small shrug and takes a moment to gather his thoughts."

    voice "9-3-36.mp3" #kujira
    bro "I just... don’t get it."

    voice "9-3-37.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Why the hell did I snap like that?"

    voice "9-3-38.mp3" #potato
    pro "Don’t worry about it. You lost control and it won’t happen again."

    voice "9-3-39.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Lost control, huh?"

    voice "9-3-40.mp3" #kujira
    bro "That’s fucking terrifying."

    voice "9-3-41.mp3" #kujira
    bro "No matter what kind of person I’m trying to be, I could just... lose control at any time?"

    voice "9-3-42.mp3" #kujira
    bro "What if I do something I regret?"
    hide bro sad2
    show bro angry3
    voice "9-3-43.mp3" #kujira
    bro "What if I almost fucking die again?"

    voice "9-3-44.mp3" #kujira
    bro "I want to live. I can see that now. But I wanted to live two days ago, too, and still ended up losing it!"

    voice "9-3-45.mp3" #kujira
    bro "How the hell can I feel safe knowing I can’t even control {i}myself?{/i}"

    voice "9-3-46.mp3" #potato
    pro "You might not believe this, but... I think I can sympathize."

    voice "9-3-47.mp3" #potato
    pro "I’m sure the drugs made it worse for you, but I still think I know what you’re feeling."
    hide bro angry3
    show bro sad2
    voice "9-3-48.mp3" #potato
    pro "Sometimes I love being alive. Everything feels breezy and fine, and I can’t even imagine being sad."

    voice "9-3-49.mp3" #potato
    pro "But then if enough things go wrong, I start to dwell on all my problems and think that the time I spent in happiness was just ignorance."

    voice "9-3-50.mp3" #potato
    pro "Even if I say right now that the good times make the bad ones worth it... what if I forget about that and do something I’ll regret forever?"

    "Or won’t get the chance to regret, rather."

    voice "9-3-51.mp3" #potato
    pro "I’ve almost been there before, and... I don’t know what’s stopping me from going back."

    voice "9-3-52.mp3" #potato
    pro "That terrifies me."

    voice "9-3-53.mp3" #kujira
    bro "...You, too, huh?"

    voice "9-3-54.mp3" #kujira
    bro "I think I needed that perspective."

    voice "9-3-55.mp3" #kujira
    bro "I wasn’t going to tell you this, but we’re being frank enough, and I think you might need to know."

    voice "9-3-56.mp3" #potato
    pro "Huh?"

    voice "9-3-57.mp3" #kujira
    bro "That night, I was really going to do it."

    voice "9-3-58.mp3" #kujira
    bro "After saying all of that to mom, hurting Maria, and getting hit like that... I lost almost every bit of sense I had."

    voice "9-3-59.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Almost."

    voice "9-3-60.mp3" #kujira
    bro "But you’ve been pretty cool this past week, you know?"

    voice "9-3-61.mp3" #kujira
    bro "It was almost too late when I realized that, but when I did, I thought of what I would have done to you if I went all the way."

    voice "9-3-62.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Right then, I knew I had to put the drugs down and hope to God that someone would find me."
    hide bro sad2
    show bro grin2
    voice "9-3-63.mp3" #kujira
    bro "So in a way, you kind of saved my life. Aside from finding me unconscious, I mean."

    voice "9-3-64.mp3" #kujira
    bro "If things start to seem bleak... I want you to remember that you’ve at least done that for me."

    voice "9-3-65.mp3" #potato
    pro "...Thanks. I will."

    voice "9-3-66.mp3" #potato
    pro "And you know, that made me think of something. I’m just spitballing here, but..."

    voice "9-3-67.mp3" #potato
    pro "Well, you know how cynics say that you can’t trust anyone but yourself?"

    voice "9-3-68.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Yeah. You think it’s just a bunch of bullshit?"

    voice "9-3-69.mp3" #potato
    pro "Worse. I think there are times when it couldn’t possibly be more wrong."

    voice "9-3-70.mp3" #potato
    pro "Sometimes, you’re the only person who you {i}can’t{/i} trust."

    voice "9-3-71.mp3" #potato
    pro "If emotions cloud your judgement, you need to reach out to other people for support, or at least think about their feelings to anchor yourself in reality."

    "God, I’m starting to sound like Diane."

    "I guess she was a part of me all along, as cheesy as it sounds."

    "Better give it a rousing finish, just like she would."

    voice "9-3-72.mp3" #potato
    pro "We’re both alive, Alex. In the time that we have left, we’re all but guaranteed to be unhappy again somewhere down the line."

    voice "9-3-73.mp3" #potato
    pro "If that gets to be too much to handle and your thoughts start to turn dark..."

    menu:

        "You need to call someone you trust.":
            jump nobodywillpickthisunlesstheyspecificallywantabadendingbutokay


