    voice "9-3-76.mp3" #potato
    pro "You can call me."
    hide bro grin2
    show bro sad2
    voice "9-3-77.mp3" #potato
    pro "There’s no way I’m going to let myself lose you."

    voice "9-3-78.mp3" #kujira
