label d9s3merge:
    show bro grin2
    voice "9-3-79.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Come to think of it, there’ve been a lot of people looking out for me, huh? There’s you, Maria, and even that Lauren girl."

    #Change the music to something more upbeat, but still peaceful

    "I feel a spark soar through my chest."

    voice "9-3-80.mp3" #potato
    pro "Oh, Lauren’s been great! She’s been... {i}really{/i} great, actually. That time when we all went to your room was her idea, and she brought me a book on drugs and withdrawal that night!"

    voice "9-3-81.mp3" #potato
    pro "She also helped me with who to ask when I was looking for you, since she knows a lot more people at school than me, and she even helped look when we found out you were in another town."

    voice "9-3-82.mp3" #potato
    pro "We really owe her a lot, but whenever I tell her that, she says she’s just being a friend. I’m not sure how to repay her."

    voice "9-3-83.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Eh? Seems like you’re overthinking it."

    voice "9-3-84.mp3" #kujira
    bro "If she’s just being a friend, then doesn’t she just expect you to be a friend back?"

    voice "9-3-85.mp3" #potato
    pro "But that’s so vague! Her idea of being a friend is so dedicated, and I don’t know how to keep up with it."

    voice "9-3-86.mp3" #kujira
    bro "I dunno, just... look out for her?"

    voice "9-3-87.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Stuff like that isn’t really about keeping score. If she’s really your friend, then shouldn’t what you need to do just come naturally?"

    voice "9-3-88.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Knowing you, you’re probably already helping her without realizing it."

    voice "9-3-89.mp3" #potato
    pro "Not true! All I’m doing is taking notes for her... and helping her with rehearsals... and...  making a dress for her to use during the play..."

    voice "9-3-90.mp3" #kujira
    bro "You’re making a {i}dress{/i} for her and think you’re a bad friend?"

    voice "9-3-91.mp3" #potato
    pro "...Shut up. That’s not... I’m leaving."

    voice "9-3-92.mp3" #kujira
    bro "To spend time with Lauren?"

    voice "9-3-93.mp3" #potato
    pro "..."

    voice "9-3-94.mp3" #potato
    pro "I’m going to go work on the dress."

    voice "9-3-95.mp3" #potato
    pro "...With Lauren."

    voice "9-3-96.mp3" #kujira
    bro "I called it."

    voice "9-3-97.mp3" #potato
    pro "Yeah, whatever, you smug little bastard. You gonna be alright all alone in here?"

    voice "9-3-98.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Eh, it sucks, but I’ll just consider it my punishment for causing so much trouble."

    voice "9-3-99.mp3" #potato
    pro "Your punishment is sitting on a bed all day?"
    hide bro grin2
    show bro grin1
    voice "9-3-100.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Exactly! I’m so glad to have someone who understands my suffering."

    voice "9-3-101.mp3" #potato
    pro "You’re a moron."

    voice "9-3-102.mp3" #kujira
    bro "Haha. Bye, Emily."

    voice "9-3-103.mp3" #potato
    pro "Later!"
    stop music fadeout 1.0
    jump day9s4
